    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is for parts or a major restoration project. It currently requires significant mechanical attention to become roadworthy, including engine diagnostics and potential transmission work. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust patches on the rocker panels, fading clear coat, and several deep scratches. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places and the electronics are inconsistent. This is a project car for someone with the tools and time to bring it back to life.",
