    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all enthusiasts and DIYers! This vehicle is ready for its next chapter and a total transformation. While it's currently in poor condition and needs significant TLC, it offers a fantastic foundation for a rewarding restoration project. If you're looking for a budget-friendly way to get a car with great bones and character to make your own, this is the one for you!",
